---
layout: layouts/page.liquid
title: Projects
description: About me.
---

<h2 class="text-2xl mb-8">Projects</h2>

<p class="prose dark:prose-light">
  During my free time I often work on some freelancing projects with some
  designer friends. You can check the open source ones (and other misc stuff) on
  <a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://github.com/jfranciscosousa">
    GitHub </a
  >.
</p>

<ul class="mt-10 space-y-8">
  {% for project in projects %}
    <li class="Project">
      <div class="flex flex-row items-center space-x-4 text-vBlue">
        <a
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="text-xl"
          href="{{ project.href }}"
          >{{ project.name }}</a
        >

        {% if project.github %}
          <a
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="Project-github"
            href="{{ project.github }}"
            aria-label="GitHub Link"
          >
            {% include "icons/github.svg" %}
          </a>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <p class="prose dark:prose-light">
        {{ project.description | markdown | safe }}
      </p>

      <small class="mt-2">
        {{ project.tags }}
      </small>
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
